title: The 'Top N' and 'Bottom N' functionalities do not work
description: When using the 'Top N' and 'Bottom N' options in the application, no data is displayed. This issue occurs when attempting to save and preview the data.
OB: The 'Top N' and 'Bottom N' options are not displaying any data when saving and previewing.
EB: The expected result is that the data should be displayed based on the selected 'Top N' and 'Input Parameters'. However, currently, no data is shown.
SR: Update the application to correctly display the data according to the selected 'Top N' and 'Input Parameters' when saving and previewing.
